#scene.startConversation( 'BlackBar', 'black-bar', [ { name: 'port1', anim: 'Ada_normal' } ] );
#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_annoyed' );
Adalais: No, I cannot get out of the room via the door.  Some idiots have blocked it off.
Adalais: Come on, think of a different answer.
#scene.endConversation();

#scene.startConversation( 'BlackBar', 'black-bar', [ { name: 'port1', anim: 'Ada_normal' } ] );
#scene.setActor( 'Adalais_act', 220, 132 );
#scene.setAnimation( 'Adalais_act', 'Ada_actor_classroom1_left' );
#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_normal' );
Adalais: Mr. Ralgo was just explaining calculus to us from this podium.  It still has a paper with his lecture notes on it.
#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_annoyed' );
Adalais: The paper simply says 'calculus' at the top, and there are a bunch of incoherent scribbles.  Also at the bottom it says 'PS remember to give pop quiz tomorrow, I've got to keep them on their toes.'
#scene.endConversation();
#scene.restoreActorBase( 'Adalais_act' );

#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_thoughtful' );
Adalais: I wonder what he was planning to do with these...
#scene.endConversation();
#scene.restoreActorBase( 'Adalais_act' );

#scene.startConversation( 'BlackBarLeft', 'black-bar-left', [ { name: 'port1', anim: 'Ada_normal' } ] );
#scene.setActor( 'Adalais_act', 142, 259 );
#scene.setAnimation( 'Adalais_act', 'Ada_actor_classroom1_right' );
#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_normal' );
Adalais: These are Mr. Ralgo's 2.1 Stereo speakers${player.get( 'cell_phone_location' ) !== 'desk' ? '.  They are powered on, but will require an AUX cable to play sound' : ''}.

#scene.startConversation( 'BlackBar', 'black-bar', [ { name: 'port1', anim: 'Ada_normal' } ] );
#scene.setActor( 'Adalais_act', 30, 180 );
Adalais: That rancid banana is still over here.  Should I pick it up again?

#scene.setConv( 'Adalais_act', 'Ada_struggle' );
Adalais: Okay, I have the rancid banana again.
#scene.endConversation();
#scene.restoreActorBase( 'Adalais_act' );

#scene.setConv( 'Adalais_act', 'Ada_normal' );
Adalais: I think I should stay away from that for now.
#scene.endConversation();
#scene.restoreActorBase( 'Adalais_act' );

#scene.startConversation( 'BlackBar', 'black-bar', [ { name: 'port1', anim: 'invisible' }, { name: 'port2', anim: 'invisible' }  ] );
#scene.setConv( 'port2', 'Ada_normal' );
Adalais: I would go look at Mr, Ralgo's speakers, except Eva and Mildrid are having a conversation over there.
#scene.setConv( 'port2', 'Ada_annoyed' );
Adalais: I do not like them very much, and I doubt that they would move at my behest, even if I asked *nicely*.
#scene.endConversation();

#scene.startConversation( 'BlackBarLeft', 'black-bar-left', [ { name: 'port1', anim: 'Ada_normal2' } ] );
#scene.setActor( 'Adalais_act', 142, 259 );
#scene.setAnimation( 'Adalais_act', 'Ada_actor_classroom1_right' );
#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_thoughtful' )
Adalais: I suppose, if I so desired, I could use Jonathan's cell phone to play music on them.

#scene.setConv( 'port1', 'Ada_normal' );
Adalais: I will just leave it alone for now.
#scene.endConversation();
#scene.restoreActorBase();
